1
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness, I will not fail
to rescue you this time.</font>

2
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:22,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Louch Brittan, White Knight 
of the Imperial First Legion!</font>

3
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:24,250
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#343531"><font size="14">White Knight of the
 Imperial First Legion
 Louch Brittan</font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness. Please wake up.</font>

5
00:00:30,460 --> 00:00:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

6
00:00:34,420 --> 00:00:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do apologize for leaving 
you in here for so long.</font>

7
00:00:37,690 --> 00:00:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took some time to 
develop my new spell.</font>

8
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, the magic 
I've come up with is flawless!</font>

9
00:00:46,230 --> 00:00:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A spell to prevent perception except 
by those who are pure of heart!</font>

10
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Upon activating the spell,</font>

11
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for a set period of time, I become 
imperceivable unless you're pure of heart.</font>

12
00:00:54,320 --> 00:00:57,910
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#000000">{\an7}Can't touch</font></b></font>

13
00:00:55,950 --> 00:00:57,910
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#000000">{\an9}Can't see</font></b></font>

14
00:00:58,380 --> 00:01:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not just limited to sight.</font>

15
00:01:01,970 --> 00:01:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The impure of heart can neither touch 
nor hear me at the moment.</font>

16
00:01:03,950 --> 00:01:08,000
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#000000">{\an7}Can't touch</font></b></font>

17
00:01:04,830 --> 00:01:05,910
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#debec6">{\an7}Swoosh</font></b></font>

18
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:08,000
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#000000">{\an9}Can't hear</font></b></font>

19
00:01:08,310 --> 00:01:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though it also means I cannot 
touch anyone who's not pure of heart.</font>

20
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, it's a bit over-the-top 
on how pure-hearted you have to be...</font>

21
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My troops who play video games too much.</font>

22
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:26,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or secretly eat snacks ended 
up being unable to notice me...</font>

23
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:28,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir Brittan?</font>

24
00:01:28,230 --> 00:01:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, you...</font>

25
00:01:29,610 --> 00:01:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that Her Highness would be affected!</font>

26
00:01:38,220 --> 00:01:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me, Your Highness.</font>

27
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wake up.</font>

28
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

29
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:27,970
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="32">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

30
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,230
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d1dbb6"><font size="15">Swoosh</font></font></b></font>

31
00:03:32,810 --> 00:03:33,730
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d1dbb6"><font size="15">Swoosh</font></font></b></font>

32
00:03:33,690 --> 00:03:33,980
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d1dbb6"><font size="15">Swoosh</font></font></b></font>

33
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't touch Her Highness...</font>

34
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This must mean...</font>

35
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The spell was a failure!</font>

36
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This spell is one where not even 
the pure of heart can perceive me!</font>

37
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should lift the spell 
for now—wait, no!</font>

38
00:03:51,570 --> 00:03:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way to lift this spell 
other than to let it run its course!</font>

39
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing out here?</font>

40
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can see me?!</font>

41
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a foolish question.</font>

42
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That night, we managed to see eye-to-eye,
thanks to <i>Mobile Cavalry Soul Cross,</i></font>

43
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we spent time after 
that discussing our favorite anime.</font>

44
00:04:21,730 --> 00:04:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never forget 
the sight of a dear friend.</font>

45
00:04:26,090 --> 00:04:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would I, Loutchi?</font>

46
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotchi!</font>

47
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

48
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic that prevents people outside 
of the intended scope from perceiving you?</font>

49
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I spent a long time 
creating that spell...</font>

50
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it didn't work.</font>

51
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:51,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did all sorts of tests to see 
if I made a mistake with the scope,</font>

52
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but not a single person noticed me.</font>

53
00:04:56,140 --> 00:04:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, <i>I</i> can see you.</font>

54
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true. I wonder why.</font>

55
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps it turned out</font>

56
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to be a spell that
only lets your friends perceive you.</font>

57
00:05:12,110 --> 00:05:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe so.</font>

58
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:17,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A spell that only lets Gotchi see me...</font>

59
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that useful for anything?</font>

60
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh right, Gotchi. What 
brings you out here at night?</font>

61
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I remember now.</font>

62
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're about to show 
the <i>Gazinder</i> movie on Hell-X TV.</font>

63
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The <i>Gazinder</i> movie?!</font>

64
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd watch it 
in the Hellholm theater room.</font>

65
00:05:40,990 --> 00:05:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about it, Loutchi?</font>

66
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to!</font>

67
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but if anyone in Hellholm 
spotted you with a human like me,</font>

68
00:05:49,170 --> 00:05:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would cause an uproar.</font>

69
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it'd be fine.</font>

70
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and besides, Loutchi.</font>

71
00:05:56,650 --> 00:06:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, you've cast 
the perfect spell on yourself, have you not?</font>

72
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! The spell 
that only lets Gotchi see me!</font>

73
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, off we go.</font>

74
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go! Go!</font>

75
00:06:14,810 --> 00:06:19,190
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="15">{\an9}<font color="#ffffff">Cosmic Supreme
 <font face="Impact"><font size="55"><i>Gazinder</i></font></font></font></font></font>

76
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:23,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watching this on a giant screen rules!</font>

77
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That it does!</font>

78
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:28,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotchi, you turned my failure 
into what will be a fond memory.</font>

79
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

80
00:06:31,090 --> 00:06:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to thank me.</font>

81
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what friends are for.</font>

82
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:43,460
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="10">{\an9}<font color="#af544f">Cosmic Supreme
 <font face="Impact"><font size="45"><i><font color="#de244b">Gazinder</font></i></font></font></font></font></font>

83
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:43,460
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

84
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Many years have passed since the
 Imperial Army and Hellhorde went to war.</i></font>

85
00:06:50,330 --> 00:06:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion</i></font>

86
00:06:55,770 --> 00:06:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>falls into the hands of the Hellhorde 
in the midst of fierce battle,</i></font>

87
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and is subjected 
to torture day in and day out.</i></font>

88
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:08,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The grand inquisitor Torture 
Tortura's torture in particular...</i></font>

89
00:07:09,290 --> 00:07:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is the very definition of merciless.</i></font>

90
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks yummy!</font>

91
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I definitely want it!</font>

92
00:07:16,570 --> 00:07:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess, if you'd like to try some...</font>

93
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As brave and dashing 
as the princess is...</i></font>

94
00:07:20,490 --> 00:07:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll have to divulge 
an imperial secret.</font>

95
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll talk!</font>

96
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She cannot stop herself 
from confessing.</i></font>

97
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious!</font>

98
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

99
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the Royal Empire 
has five neighborhood cats.</font>

100
00:07:36,890 --> 00:07:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've managed to obtain 
a fantastic secret.</font>

101
00:07:40,590 --> 00:07:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today, let's take a peek into 
a day in the life of this torturer.</i></font>

102
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So warm...</font>

103
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:58,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, how shameful of me.</font>

104
00:07:58,270 --> 00:08:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Visiting my parents after so long 
has made me drop my guard.</font>

105
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:04,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ordered it to the wrong address!</font>

106
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just stopping by my parents' to fetch
the package I accidentally sent them.</font>

107
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:14,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a torture session after this, 
so I need to snap out of it!</font>

108
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do some cleaning in here 
to wake myself up.</font>

109
00:08:21,090 --> 00:08:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found it.</font>

110
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the package, right?</font>

111
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had the wrong idea, 
so I'd brought it to my bedroom.</font>

112
00:08:29,410 --> 00:08:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a total goner!</font>

113
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leaving everything within arm's reach!</font>

114
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Folding a cushion over 
to use as a pillow!</font>

115
00:08:37,450 --> 00:08:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Sh-She's a total goner!</font>

116
00:08:40,570 --> 00:08:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it.</font>

117
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was trying to clean up, 
when I found some snacks...</font>

118
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,830
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="10"><font color="#5b557a">Yuki no Ya</font></font></b></font>

119
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,960
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d0122e">Kiratto-san</font></b></font>

120
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Came across some manga I used to like...</font>

121
00:08:49,350 --> 00:08:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found some photos which 
got me nostalgic...</font>

122
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which made me want to 
dig up my yearbook...</font>

123
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I wanted to try on my 
uniform to see if still fit...</font>

124
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And before I knew it...</font>

125
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ended up like this.</font>

126
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you did, huh?</font>

127
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to tell me.</font>

128
00:09:09,190 --> 00:09:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I can't stay in here.</font>

129
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I don't leave soon...</font>

130
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't make it in time 
for today's torture...</font>

131
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why...</font>

132
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bananas being thrown 
by the buff koala...</font>

133
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

134
00:09:22,870 --> 00:09:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I want to catch them all 
while standing on a stool...</font>

135
00:09:31,710 --> 00:09:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was I asleep just now?</font>

136
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think so.</font>

137
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no. I need to wake up...</font>

138
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't escape the warm kotatsu...</font>

139
00:09:46,170 --> 00:09:49,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It bids me into the world of dreams!</font>

140
00:09:49,940 --> 00:09:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bear it, Torture!</font>

141
00:09:52,370 --> 00:09:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

142
00:09:54,210 --> 00:09:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh oh. Mom's turned into Kiratto-san.</font>

143
00:09:57,520 --> 00:10:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels like I'm wandering between 
the real and dream world.</font>

144
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I need to wake up, 
but I'm slowly getting sleepier...</font>

145
00:10:04,970 --> 00:10:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sleepy, sleepy, sleepy...</font>

146
00:10:07,450 --> 00:10:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah. What's in this package?</font>

147
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The torture implement I was 
going to use for today's torture.</font>

148
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna be tortured with this!</font>

149
00:10:20,930 --> 00:10:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sleepy, sleepy, sleepy...</font>

150
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right, it's the torture implement 
I picked out with the princess...</font>

151
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:30,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should arrive on the 22nd.</font>

152
00:10:30,690 --> 00:10:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome! Thanks!</font>

153
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait!</font>

154
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today's the day the princess was...</i></font>

155
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looking forward to...</i></font>

156
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looking forward to...</i></font>

157
00:10:47,990 --> 00:10:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looking forward to!</i></font>

158
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sleepy!</font>

159
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If today's torture is canceled...</font>

160
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The princess would be so sad!</font>

161
00:10:58,430 --> 00:11:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making your torture target sad is...</font>

162
00:11:01,290 --> 00:11:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unthinkable for a torturer!</font>

163
00:11:07,470 --> 00:11:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a safe trip back.</font>

164
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be going!</font>

165
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem awfully chipper 
today, Your Highness.</font>

166
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep.</font>

167
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking forward to 
today's torture for ages!</font>

168
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A torture you've been 
looking forward to for ages?</font>

169
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you waiting, Princess.</font>

170
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you are, Torture.</font>

171
00:11:33,620 --> 00:11:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Without further ado...</font>

172
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Tis time for torture!</font>

173
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:41,510
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="15"><font color="#314148">Entrance
Ceremony</font></font></b></font></font>

174
00:11:41,890 --> 00:11:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boss? What's wrong? You seem down.</font>

175
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, I haven't been 
able to see my daughter...</font>

176
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sounds like it's something 
pretty serious!</i></font>

177
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:57,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

178
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Totchan's coming home today?!</font>

179
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to see her!</font>

180
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you have work, dear?</font>

181
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she's only stopping 
by to pick up a package.</font>

182
00:12:08,450 --> 00:12:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care how long! I want to see her!</font>

183
00:12:11,170 --> 00:12:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so desperate to see her?</font>

184
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't seen her for 
three whole weeks now!</font>

185
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not that long 
for a daughter who's moved out.</font>

186
00:12:19,010 --> 00:12:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

187
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and leave already 
or else you'll be late to work.</font>

188
00:12:25,170 --> 00:12:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm supposed to be working 
for the sake of my family...</font>

189
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why must I sacrifice my family 
for the sake of my work?!</font>

190
00:12:32,540 --> 00:12:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Save the dramatics 
for something more serious.</font>

191
00:12:35,310 --> 00:12:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A photo!</font>

192
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least get me a photo!</font>

193
00:12:39,130 --> 00:12:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to see how much 
my daughter's grown!</font>

194
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:48,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think an adult woman's 
got much growing to do.</font>

195
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,160
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#3e523a">{\an7}I'd like that photo sooner rather than later...</font></font>

196
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,160
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#44503f">{\an7}Sure thing</font></font>

197
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#3e523a">{\an7}I'd like that photo sooner rather than later...</font></font>

198
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#44503f">{\an7}Sure thing</font></font>

199
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:55,920
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#44503f">{\an7}Here's the photo</font></font>

200
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,670
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#44503f">{\an7}Sure thing</font></font>

201
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,670
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#44503f">{\an7}Here's the photo</font></font>

202
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:05,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! Time to work my butt off!</font>

203
00:13:05,650 --> 00:13:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He cheered up.</i></font>

204
00:13:10,890 --> 00:13:12,930
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

205
00:13:16,050 --> 00:13:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going out pretty far today, right?</font>

206
00:13:18,180 --> 00:13:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep.</font>

207
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw a pancake place 
that looked good in a magazine,</font>

208
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:25,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I wanted to torture 
the princess there.</font>

209
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't been there yet, 
have you, Vanilla-chan?</font>

210
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you be okay? You won't get lost?</font>

211
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we have our maid drive you two?</font>

212
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, this is my torture.</font>

213
00:13:37,010 --> 00:13:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be one to escort the princess there!</font>

214
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Vanilla-chan!</i></font>

215
00:13:42,050 --> 00:13:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm leaving!</font>

216
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have fun now!</font>

217
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's growing up so quickly.</font>

218
00:13:50,010 --> 00:13:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

219
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before you know it, 
our baby bird will be leaving the nest.</font>

220
00:13:54,890 --> 00:13:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

221
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:57,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

222
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's disguise ourselves and follow her!</font>

223
00:14:03,770 --> 00:14:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get the car ready, Miss Kon!</font>

224
00:14:05,940 --> 00:14:07,360
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#78a6b4">Yes, sir</font></font></b></font>

225
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:14,160
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="9"><font color="#5e6b79">Kuroenji 
Station</font></font></b></font></font>

226
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, s-sorry I'm late.</font>

227
00:14:15,490 --> 00:14:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No worries, I just got here myself.</font>

228
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a relief.</font>

229
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we get going?</font>

230
00:14:21,890 --> 00:14:23,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! It's this way.</font>

231
00:14:28,010 --> 00:14:29,760
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an7}<b><font color="#f07c65"><font size="25">Helltrianon</font></font></b></font>

232
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:31,760
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font color="#cd9aa0"><b><font size="15">phell</font></b></font></font>

233
00:14:42,050 --> 00:14:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's supposed to be a
five-minute walk from the station,</font>

234
00:14:44,730 --> 00:14:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they've been walking 
for twenty minutes now.</font>

235
00:14:47,370 --> 00:14:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as I feared, Vanilla-chan is lost!</font>

236
00:14:51,710 --> 00:14:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way, Princess!</font>

237
00:14:54,020 --> 00:14:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

238
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

239
00:14:57,190 --> 00:15:00,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My shoelaces came loose. 
Mind if I tie them back up over there?</font>

240
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead.</font>

241
00:15:02,700 --> 00:15:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why won't the princess lead the way?!</font>

242
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't she see that 
Vanilla-chan's in distress?!</font>

243
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, dear. Didn't you notice?</font>

244
00:15:11,820 --> 00:15:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

245
00:15:13,310 --> 00:15:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just now, the princess, 
while appearing to be walking naturally,</font>

246
00:15:17,730 --> 00:15:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">caught her shoelaces with her foot...</font>

247
00:15:20,090 --> 00:15:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and untied them!</font>

248
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

249
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the spot she chose 
to tie them...</font>

250
00:15:25,490 --> 00:15:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is next to a giant map!</font>

251
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:29,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right!</font>

252
00:15:29,780 --> 00:15:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In addition, so far on their walk...</font>

253
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She took the outer side on narrow back 
streets so Vanilla-chan's safe from cars,</font>

254
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:40,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">subtly made sure that she 
was hydrating regularly...</font>

255
00:15:40,910 --> 00:15:47,250
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Georgia"><font size="10"><b><font color="#c9e0e8">Kuroenji
Station</font></b></font></font></font>

256
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:47,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what's more, she arrived ahead of 
schedule to scope out a map of the area!</font>

257
00:15:47,530 --> 00:15:49,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She did all that?!</font>

258
00:15:49,130 --> 00:15:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The princess is well aware</font>

259
00:15:51,690 --> 00:15:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of the fact that Vanilla-chan 
has lost her way...</font>

260
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As well as...</font>

261
00:15:55,370 --> 00:15:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-chan's desire to 
be the one to guide her!</font>

262
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess!</font>

263
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured it out, Princess!</font>

264
00:16:08,260 --> 00:16:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's this way!</font>

265
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

266
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here!</font>

267
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We made it!</font>

268
00:16:22,380 --> 00:16:24,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, Vanilla-chan.</font>

269
00:16:24,250 --> 00:16:26,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh!</font>

270
00:16:26,540 --> 00:16:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time for your torture, Princess!</font>

271
00:16:29,340 --> 00:16:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't give in so easily!</font>

272
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

273
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They look great!</font>

274
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

275
00:16:47,350 --> 00:16:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla-chan, wanna try some of mine?</font>

276
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:51,360
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}They were so tasty,
she forgot to ask for a secret</font></b></font></font>

277
00:16:49,260 --> 00:16:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, can I?</font>

278
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, open wide.</font>

279
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:55,360
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

280
00:17:02,010 --> 00:17:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is her playmate one of 
her friends from preschool?</font>

281
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, she just met him today.</font>

282
00:17:08,820 --> 00:17:09,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

283
00:17:09,930 --> 00:17:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's amazing that she can get along 
with someone she met just now by chance.</font>

284
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to step away 
to do some shopping.</font>

285
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep an eye on her.</font>

286
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later.</font>

287
00:17:23,420 --> 00:17:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I should find somewhere to sit.</font>

288
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:29,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe there's a bench over here.</font>

289
00:17:31,820 --> 00:17:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hello there.</font>

290
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

291
00:17:35,470 --> 00:17:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He must be that child's father.</i></font>

292
00:17:38,230 --> 00:17:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for playing with my child.</font>

293
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh no, I should be thanking you.</font>

294
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I say to him?</i></font>

295
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm pretty good at talking to people 
I've just met without getting nervous,</i></font>

296
00:18:04,580 --> 00:18:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the problem is I don't 
know what to talk about.</i></font>

297
00:18:07,740 --> 00:18:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If we were colleagues, we'd have 
things in common I could bring up...</i></font>

298
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:18,530
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font color="#3f4349">Work work work</font></b></font>

299
00:18:11,950 --> 00:18:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he's not part of the Hellhorde.</i></font>

300
00:18:14,770 --> 00:18:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I even say to someone I've met 
for the first time today?</i></font>

301
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Do you live around here?"</i></font>

302
00:18:22,300 --> 00:18:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, is it okay to ask something 
so personal right off the bat?</i></font>

303
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Great weather we're having."</i></font>

304
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It'd be too obvious that 
I'm at a loss for conversation.</i></font>

305
00:18:32,390 --> 00:18:35,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"What anime are you 
watching this season?"</i></font>

306
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no guarantee that he likes anime.</i></font>

307
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've got nothing to talk about 
other than work and anime!</i></font>

308
00:18:44,170 --> 00:18:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't have any problem 
talking to Loutchi...</i></font>

309
00:18:47,250 --> 00:18:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotchi...</font>

310
00:18:48,930 --> 00:18:51,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My son's in first grade.</font>

311
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your daughter around his age?</font>

312
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

313
00:18:55,880 --> 00:18:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To start a conversation, you should 
first offer information about yourself.</i></font>

314
00:19:00,500 --> 00:19:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, she's still in preschool, 
but I'm sad that she'll be moving up soon.</font>

315
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it really is so sad, isn't it?</font>

316
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm doing a good job talking to him!</i></font>

317
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How has school been?</font>

318
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I managed to expand on the topic!</i></font>

319
00:19:18,660 --> 00:19:20,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Two combo!</i></font>

320
00:19:22,110 --> 00:19:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Once the game of verbal 
catch is underway,</i></font>

321
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just need to keep 
the conversation going!</i></font>

322
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not easy, that's for sure.</font>

323
00:19:30,370 --> 00:19:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a music recital we just had, 
all the kids needed matching T-shirts,</font>

324
00:19:35,410 --> 00:19:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they only gave us five days' notice.</font>

325
00:19:38,060 --> 00:19:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Only five days?</font>

326
00:19:40,870 --> 00:19:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It had to be a solid yellow T-shirt, too.</font>

327
00:19:43,410 --> 00:19:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like, you're really springing 
that on us with five days?</font>

328
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sure sounds rough.</font>

329
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm doing it!</i></font>

330
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Three combo!</i></font>

331
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As we continue to work in tandem...</i></font>

332
00:20:02,090 --> 00:20:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Four combo!</i></font>

333
00:20:05,180 --> 00:20:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're building up a conversation combo!</i></font>

334
00:20:08,190 --> 00:20:12,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's so nice and easy to talk to!</i></font>

335
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of T-shirts, I can't wear them 
with these horns on my shoulders.</font>

336
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Five combo!</i></font>

337
00:20:22,610 --> 00:20:25,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's true. They'd get all torn up.</font>

338
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

339
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so sad that I can't wear 
T-shirts of my favorite anime.</font>

340
00:20:36,780 --> 00:20:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Bad!</i></font>

341
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I messed up!</i></font>

342
00:20:40,290 --> 00:20:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our lively conversation lowered my guard, 
and I said the word "anime!"</i></font>

343
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's a nice person. 
Even if he's not very familiar...</i></font>

344
00:20:49,320 --> 00:20:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to watch anime as a kid, too.</font>

345
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:56,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's sure to change the topic 
to cater to my hobbies, like so.</i></font>

346
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that will lead to...</i></font>

347
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Recent anime?</font>

348
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:02,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

349
00:21:02,980 --> 00:21:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I just watch what 
my son does nowadays.</font>

350
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Makes sense...</font>

351
00:21:12,170 --> 00:21:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our different power levels will turn 
the conversation hazy, like a cloud!</i></font>

352
00:21:18,490 --> 00:21:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just when it had gotten so lively, too!</i></font>

353
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you... like anime?</font>

354
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes.</font>

355
00:21:30,870 --> 00:21:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha...</font>

356
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:36,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you watching this season?</font>

357
00:21:36,020 --> 00:21:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

358
00:21:44,570 --> 00:21:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Six c-c-c-c-combo!</i></font>

359
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh?</font>

360
00:21:49,860 --> 00:21:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

361
00:21:51,080 --> 00:21:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be that you...</font>

362
00:21:54,010 --> 00:21:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm into anime.</font>

363
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seven combo!</i></font>

364
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eight combo! Nine combo!</i></font>

365
00:22:08,340 --> 00:22:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ten combo!</i></font>

366
00:22:12,470 --> 00:22:14,930
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="15"><b><font color="#1a191c">{\an8}The Hell-Lord 
talked</font></b></font></font>

